description: These are a few other holidays that didn’t have enough emoticons to get their own full category, so I bundled them together here. There are options for Mother’s Day, someone’s wedding, April Fool’s, Valentine’s day, and anything you are celebrating that deserves a congratulations. Send these holiday emoticons to your loved ones to help celebrate a special day.
